    REQUIREMENTS

-Python 3.5+
-Pygame

    INSTALLATION
After installing Python, Pygame and PIP, at the terminal type the following command:

    pip install pygame_gui

    UPDATE TO THE LATEST VERSION
Run this command on the terminal:

    pip install pygame_gui -U

    UNINSTALL
Run this command on the terminal:

    pip3 uninstall pygame_gui

    Source: https://github.com/MyreMylar/pygame_gui